00:22:18,836 --> 00:22:25,778
do you remember what you said in my office over a decade ago?

255
00:22:25,778 --> 00:22:29,580
Mr. Shi, it's been so many years. I can't remember. Remind me.

256
00:22:30,300 --> 00:22:31,899
At the time, you said...

257
00:22:31,899 --> 00:22:35,680
Xiaoming was too young to be well-seasoned.

258
00:22:35,680 --> 00:22:42,559
He would make wrong decisions in the management capacity due to inexperience.

259
00:22:51,300 --> 00:22:52,780
Shi Yan,

260
00:22:52,780 --> 00:22:56,119
these gentlemen have always cared for you.

261
00:22:56,119 --> 00:22:57,880
Regarding their criticism,

262
00:22:57,880 --> 00:23:00,780
if it's true, make corrections.

263
00:23:00,780 --> 00:23:02,920
If it's a misunderstanding, make improvements.

264
00:23:06,839 --> 00:23:15,039
Cloud Innovation needs many people's protection and guidance to grow into a giant empire.

265
00:23:26,160 --> 00:23:28,440
Thank you, gentlemen, for all your concern.

266
00:23:28,440 --> 00:23:32,860
The choices to invest in Le'an Tech and Juhe were my own decisions.

267
00:23:32,860 --> 00:23:35,440
I'm fully responsible.

268
00:23:35,440 --> 00:23:41,140
I will think of a solution to Le'an's issue soon, and stop you from worrying.

269
00:23:41,140 --> 00:23:43,589
Zheng Shuyi's always been following this project.

270
00:23:43,589 --> 00:23:46,619
No one is better suited than her for this project.

271
00:23:47,820 --> 00:23:50,780
I won't miss any issue deadlines.

272
00:23:52,880 --> 00:23:56,191
I can't make this arrangement.

273
00:23:58,000 --> 00:24:00,379
I will have a good talk with her.

274
00:24:08,559 --> 00:24:10,939
He doesn't want to see me now.

275
00:24:10,939 --> 00:24:12,760
He even blacklisted me.

276
00:24:12,760 --> 00:24:14,839
He doesn't reply to my emails.

277
00:24:14,839 --> 00:24:16,920
I'm totally helpless.

278
00:24:17,599 --> 00:24:21,240
I just hope it won't affect our collaboration on this project.

279
00:24:22,079 --> 00:24:24,839
How come?

280
00:24:24,839 --> 00:24:27,300
Why didn't you say it earlier...

281
00:24:29,920 --> 00:24:32,019
I don't know what to do now.

282
00:24:32,019 --> 00:24:36,559
 Now, I can't comfort you by pretending to feel the same. 

283
00:24:37,079 --> 00:24:43,079
All I can say is things are already like this.

284
00:24:43,079 --> 00:24:44,700
Do you know?

285
00:24:44,700 --> 00:24:46,900
He even sent his niece away.

286
00:24:46,900 --> 00:24:49,140
He doesn't want her near me.

287
00:24:49,140 --> 00:24:52,480
 He completely doesn't want to hear anything about me anymore. 

288
00:24:52,480 --> 00:24:54,900
Don't be too sad.

289
00:24:54,900 --> 00:24:58,219
Maybe you can find a way to meet him. It's easier to talk in person.

290
00:24:58,219 --> 00:25:01,239
I don't have the courage to see him.

291
00:25:01,239 --> 00:25:05,460
Just thinking he doesn't want to see me makes me feel awful.

292
00:25:05,460 --> 00:25:06,620
Then don't think about him.

293
00:25:06,620 --> 00:25:10,359
Think about Yue Xingzhou and that Qin... Qin something.

294
00:25:10,359 --> 00:25:11,820
 They're really suffering. 

295
00:25:11,820 --> 00:25:14,599
 They must've lost all their appetite and sleep now. 

296
00:25:14,599 --> 00:25:20,259
How about this? After work, go home, take a bath, order some crayfish, and watch some variety shows.

297
00:25:20,259 --> 00:25:23,399
Sleep on it, and maybe things will turn around.

298
00:25:23,399 --> 00:25:25,340
It's impossible.

299
00:25:25,340 --> 00:25:28,859
Our relationship has ended.

300
00:25:29,620 --> 00:25:30,640
All right, I won't talk anymore.

301
00:25:30,640 --> 00:25:32,359
I'm working.

302
00:25:58,160 --> 00:25:59,899
You've thought it over?

303
00:26:00,599 --> 00:26:04,000
It's best for my colleagues to take over Cloud Innovation's project.

304
00:26:04,000 --> 00:26:05,459
I will ensure a smooth handover.

305
00:26:05,459 --> 00:26:08,240
If they need my help, I will do my best.

306
00:26:08,240 --> 00:26:10,319
There's no need for credit.

307
00:26:10,319 --> 00:26:14,939
I just hope Cloud Innovation's project can continue.

308
00:26:17,680 --> 00:26:19,480
Then let's do as you said.

309
00:26:19,480 --> 00:26:22,039
Organize your documents.

310
00:26:22,039 --> 00:26:24,100
I will arrange the handover.

311
00:26:25,319 --> 00:26:26,880
Okay.

312
00:26:37,720 --> 00:26:39,200
Shuyi,

313
00:26:39,200 --> 00:26:41,580
what did the chief editor say to you?

314
00:26:42,160 --> 00:26:44,480
I will hand over the Cloud Innovation project.

315
00:26:44,480 --> 00:26:46,340
What?

316
00:26:46,340 --> 00:26:50,020
Just hearing it makes me feel bad for you.

317
00:26:51,580 --> 00:26:54,680
It must be Xu Yuling who said something to the lead editor.

318
00:26:54,680 --> 00:26:56,640
Otherwise, the chief editor wouldn't make this arrangement.

319
00:26:56,640 --> 00:27:00,480
She doesn't understand Cloud Innovation at all. How can she do the project well?

320
00:27:10,340 --> 00:27:12,659
What's happening with Cloud Innovation?

321
00:27:12,659 --> 00:27:15,680
Why does Shuyi have to give up the Cloud Innovation project?

322
00:27:16,720 --> 00:27:18,419
What?

323
00:27:19,119 --> 00:27:21,680
When did they get together?

324
00:27:22,200 --> 00:27:24,859
Then, why did they have a falling out?

325
00:27:46,079 --> 00:27:49,020
Hello, students. Today, we'll talk about secondary markets.

326
00:27:49,020 --> 00:27:51,440
Let's look at the big screen.

327
00:27:51,839 --> 00:27:53,839
What is a secondary market?

328
00:27:57,499 --> 00:28:00,400
You put two accident reports of Zhanlan in the featured project.

329
00:28:00,400 --> 00:28:01,939
And they are different.

330
00:28:01,939 --> 00:28:06,119
It's a waste of my time looking at this stuff.

331
00:28:07,979 --> 00:28:10,956
Zhanlan is a company Cloud Innovation once intended to invest in.

332
00:28:10,956 --> 00:28:14,400
I've already marked the reasons for the differences in the document.

333
00:28:14,400 --> 00:28:15,459
You can check carefully.

334
00:28:15,459 --> 00:28:16,920
No need, thank you.

335
00:28:16,920 --> 00:28:19,079
I rely on myself.

336
00:28:19,079 --> 00:28:21,179
I have my own work method.

337
00:28:21,179 --> 00:28:25,559
To do a project well requires the reporter's in-depth first-hand observation.

338
00:28:25,559 --> 00:28:27,900
Your tricks won't play well.

339
00:28:28,799 --> 00:28:29,640
What are you implying?

340
00:28:29,640 --> 00:28:31,559
Nothing.

341
00:28:31,559 --> 00:28:35,640
You think I don't know how you got the project from Shi Yan?

342
00:28:38,119 --> 00:28:42,319
Opportunities gained through dirty tricks will eventually be lost.

343
00:28:45,680 --> 00:28:49,200
Cloud Innovation's project will have nothing to do with you in the future.

344
00:29:02,759 --> 00:29:04,259
Send the materials to my email later.

345
00:29:04,259 --> 00:29:06,060
Then notify Guan Ji and Yu You.

346
00:29:06,060 --> 00:29:07,720
Got it, Mr. Shi.

347
00:29:08,720 --> 00:29:10,259
Mr. Shi, hello.

348
00:29:10,259 --> 00:29:12,920
Long time no see. Do you remember me?

349
00:29:14,480 --> 00:29:16,599
I'm Xu Yuling, a reporter from Financial Introduce.

350
00:29:16,599 --> 00:29:20,039
I will be in charge of the Cloud Innovation project.

351
00:29:20,039 --> 00:29:21,160
Ms. Xu, please return.

352
00:29:21,160 --> 00:29:24,680
The collaboration between Cloud Innovation and Financial Introduce has ended.

353
00:29:25,920 --> 00:29:26,759
Mr. Shi,

354
00:29:26,759 --> 00:29:28,219
I've done a lot of preparatory work.

355
00:29:28,219 --> 00:29:31,100
My articles will definitely increase Cloud Innovation's publicity.

356
00:29:31,100 --> 00:29:33,680
I won't take up too much of your time.

357
00:29:34,979 --> 00:29:37,842
 Mr. Shi, I had an interview with you scheduled for this afternoon. 

358
00:29:37,842 --> 00:29:39,820
 Mr. Shi is going out. Ms. Zheng, please return. 

359
00:29:39,820 --> 00:29:41,060
 Today's interview is already over. 

360
00:29:41,060 --> 00:29:43,380
 I've been looking forward to this interview for a long time. 

361
00:29:43,380 --> 00:29:45,219
 Finally, the day has come. 

362
00:29:45,219 --> 00:29:47,980
 Can you spare some time now? 

363
00:29:50,820 --> 00:29:55,039
 It will just take up a little bit of your time. Okay? 

364
00:29:58,240 --> 00:30:01,359
I won't accept interviews from two reporters on the same project.

365
00:30:01,359 --> 00:30:02,580
Thank you but no.

366
00:30:02,580 --> 00:30:05,540
Mr. Shi, if you don't have time, I can interview other colleagues.

367
00:30:05,540 --> 00:30:07,559
Please give me a chance!

368
00:30:07,559 --> 00:30:10,599
Sorry, Ms. Xu, we really can't help.

369
00:30:10,599 --> 00:30:13,499
Mr. Chen, I really won't take up too much of his time.

370
00:30:13,499 --> 00:30:14,720
Please arrange it for me.

371
00:30:14,720 --> 00:30:16,640
I can interview your colleagues, can I?

372
00:30:16,640 --> 00:30:17,860
I'm sorry.

373
00:30:17,860 --> 00:30:19,159
I...

374
00:30:19,659 --> 00:30:22,500
Ms. Xu, let me escort you downstairs.

375
00:30:25,240 --> 00:30:27,759
Will you spare a few minutes?

376
00:30:46,960 --> 00:30:51,019
Shuyi, Xu Yuling went to Cloud Innovation?

377
00:30:51,680 --> 00:30:53,519
Then, how can you remain so calm?

378
00:30:53,519 --> 00:30:56,300
She must have interviewed Shi Yan.

379
00:30:56,300 --> 00:30:58,559
No! You must take back the project.

380
00:30:58,559 --> 00:31:00,559
It's your hard work.

381
00:31:01,540 --> 00:31:03,339
No need.

382
00:31:03,339 --> 00:31:07,219
As long as the project goes smoothly, whoever does it is the same.

383
00:31:22,359 --> 00:31:23,879
Why are you here?

384
00:31:23,879 --> 00:31:25,580
I came to pick you up from work.

385
00:31:26,319 --> 00:31:29,200
Go home. I'm going home to write articles, too.

386
00:31:30,799 --> 00:31:34,659
What if I say I can help you find inspiration?

387
00:31:34,659 --> 00:31:36,039
I'm a professional journalist.

388
00:31:36,039 --> 00:31:38,839
I don't need unprofessional methods to find inspiration.

389
00:31:38,839 --> 00:31:40,780
Are you sure?

390
00:32:00,319 --> 00:32:02,059
Shuyi?

391
00:32:06,524 --> 00:32:09,379
Isn't the person next to her...

392
00:32:09,379 --> 00:32:12,000
Yi Yang from Dark Horse Technology?

393
00:32:12,745 --> 00:32:16,172
Good for her! A talented man and a beautiful woman. A match made in heaven!

394
00:32:16,172 --> 00:32:19,707
Seriously? They don't look the part.

395
00:32:19,707 --> 00:32:23,580
Why would Ms. Zheng be with him?

396
00:32:23,580 --> 00:32:25,760
What's the problem?

397
00:32:25,760 --> 00:32:30,300
Only Mr. Shi can accept interviews from others, but Shuyi can't be with someone else, huh?

398
00:32:30,300 --> 00:32:32,931
When did Mr. Shi accept someone else's interview?

399
00:32:32,931 --> 00:32:37,179
Mr. Shi didn't even give Ms. Xu a chance for an interview at all.

400
00:32:37,179 --> 00:32:39,837
He didn't give her a chance? But she always goes to your company.

401
00:32:39,837 --> 00:32:42,380
Since it's not Mr. Shi, is she interviewing you?

402
00:32:42,380 --> 00:32:43,959
No.

403
00:32:43,959 --> 00:32:46,580
How could it be me?

404
00:32:46,580 --> 00:32:49,129
Do you know how much Shuyi has put into this project?

405
00:32:49,129 --> 00:32:51,580
Mr. Shi just ends the collaboration on a whim.

406
00:32:51,580 --> 00:32:54,279
He's really heartless.

407
00:32:54,279 --> 00:32:58,219
The way I see it, dating is supposed to be happy and joyful.

408
00:32:58,219 --> 00:33:00,380
I find Yi Yang quite good.

409
00:33:00,380 --> 00:33:01,979
He's handsome and considerate.

410
00:33:01,979 --> 00:33:04,580
And he finds time to please his girlfriend.

411
00:33:04,580 --> 00:33:08,719
Mr. Shi must have his reasons.

412
00:33:08,719 --> 00:33:12,219
Do you really think he's quite good?

413
00:33:13,960 --> 00:33:15,820
Quite good, indeed.

414
00:33:19,300 --> 00:33:22,740
But I already have my own boyfriend.

415
00:33:24,133 --> 00:33:25,900
Let's go eat then.

416
00:33:25,900 --> 00:33:26,839
Okay.

417
00:33:26,839 --> 00:33:28,440
Let's go.

418
00:33:31,312 --> 00:33:32,499
Weren't we here to find inspiration?

419
00:33:32,499 --> 00:33:34,010
Why are we shopping now?

420
00:33:34,010 --> 00:33:35,330
It's still early.

421
00:33:35,330 --> 00:33:37,219
How about a movie?

422
00:33:37,799 --> 00:33:39,359
Yi Yang.

423
00:33:39,892 --> 00:33:43,040
You don't like it? Then how about we go to the night market?

424
00:33:43,040 --> 00:33:46,280
I don't like night markets, nor do I need to buy anything.

425
00:33:46,280 --> 00:33:49,939
Don't girls usually like night markets?

426
00:33:51,280 --> 00:33:53,060
Maybe you'll find something you want to buy.

427
00:33:53,060 --> 00:33:54,739
I'm no ordinary girl.

428
00:33:54,739 --> 00:33:58,500
Who finds inspiration while shopping. I have absolutely no inspiration.

429
00:34:01,680 --> 00:34:04,420
Sorry. I really have work to do.

430
00:34:04,420 --> 00:34:06,200
I'm going home.

431
00:34:06,960 --> 00:34:11,540
If this place can't give you inspiration, let's go somewhere else.

432
00:34:14,159 --> 00:34:15,979
Come on, punch towards the targets.

433
00:34:15,979 --> 00:34:17,719
One, two. Good.

434
00:34:17,719 --> 00:34:18,900
One, two, three.

435
00:34:18,900 --> 00:34:20,659
Nice.

436
00:34:20,659 --> 00:34:22,660
Continue, switch positions.

437
00:34:23,280 --> 00:34:24,400
One, two, three. Continue.

438
00:34:24,400 --> 00:34:26,119
One, two, three. Continue.

439
00:34:26,800 --> 00:34:28,980
Switch, one, two.

440
00:34:28,980 --> 00:34:30,519
One, two.

441
00:34:30,519 --> 00:34:32,279
One, two, three.

442
00:34:32,279 --> 00:34:34,020
One, two, three.

443
00:34:34,020 --> 00:34:35,320
One, two, three, four.

444
00:34:35,320 --> 00:34:36,320
Good, continue. One, two, three, four.

445
00:34:36,320 --> 00:34:37,400
Good, continue. One, two, three, four.

446
00:34:37,400 --> 00:34:38,839
Switch.

447
00:34:38,839 --> 00:34:40,599
One, two.

448
00:35:00,159 --> 00:35:02,060
How's that?

449
00:35:02,060 --> 00:35:04,860
Pretty exhilarating, thank you.

450
00:35:09,119 --> 00:35:13,739
Now, you've punched away all the troubles, and inspiration will naturally come arrive.

451
00:35:13,739 --> 00:35:16,859
If you're ever unhappy, just come to me.

452
00:35:16,859 --> 00:35:19,339
I'll be your sandbag.

453
00:35:24,960 --> 00:35:26,667
Mr. Shi, hello.

454
00:35:35,159 --> 00:35:36,680
She's here again.

455
00:35:36,680 --> 00:35:38,978
She's too diligent to be good.

456
00:35:38,978 --> 00:35:42,759
She's not going to bombard us with repetitive questions the whole afternoon again. Right?

457
00:35:42,759 --> 00:35:44,900
It's such a waste of time.

458
00:35:44,900 --> 00:35:48,280
Ms. Zheng's clearly categorized the information.

459
00:35:49,280 --> 00:35:54,199
Tell her not to come again. And ask the agency to not send other people.

460
00:35:59,219 --> 00:36:03,000
Remember to review the topics we touched upon today at home.

461
00:36:03,719 --> 00:36:07,179
All right, let's call it a day.

