00:37:32,840 --> 00:37:37,400
Shuyi, do you want to ask if Shi Yan is all right?

481
00:37:40,039 --> 00:37:43,079
Are you and Shi Yan together?

482
00:37:44,119 --> 00:37:46,400
We just started dating.

483
00:37:46,400 --> 00:37:50,000
But now, it might be over.

484
00:37:52,400 --> 00:37:54,860
Shi Yan is not a grudge holder.

485
00:37:55,320 --> 00:38:00,000
Though he usually looks aloof, he wouldn't get angry easily.

486
00:38:00,000 --> 00:38:01,760
He must care about you a lot.

487
00:38:01,760 --> 00:38:03,639
That's why he's like this.

488
00:38:03,639 --> 00:38:06,760
Talk to him, clarify things, and it will be all right.

489
00:38:07,880 --> 00:38:10,340
I've already apologized to him.

490
00:38:10,340 --> 00:38:12,639
But he blocked me.

491
00:38:12,639 --> 00:38:15,380
I haven't been able to contact him since.

492
00:38:16,199 --> 00:38:18,640
How did you apologize?

493
00:38:18,640 --> 00:38:20,320
I...

494
00:38:23,800 --> 00:38:25,700
After listening to you, I think... maybe...

495
00:38:25,700 --> 00:38:32,639
He's angry because, after all this, you only care about your work and ignore his feelings.

496
00:38:34,440 --> 00:38:37,779
You're right. It's my fault.

497
00:38:37,779 --> 00:38:41,300
I was thinking about the solutions to and the impacts of our fall-out.

498
00:38:41,300 --> 00:38:47,179
But I didn't consider his feelings as his girlfriend.

499
00:38:48,860 --> 00:38:51,200
That's terrible.

500
00:38:52,760 --> 00:38:56,420
Now that you understand, you know what to do.

501
00:38:58,719 --> 00:39:00,940
Thank you, Yu You.

502
00:39:02,800 --> 00:39:07,819
But I didn't expect you to be so adept at handling romantic problems.

503
00:39:08,840 --> 00:39:13,559
Actually, I just realized recently that theory is meaningless when it comes to love.

504
00:39:13,559 --> 00:39:17,080
Being in a relationship, you can only follow your heart.

505
00:39:17,080 --> 00:39:19,899
That's right. Preconceptions are useless.

506
00:39:19,899 --> 00:39:24,500
I never thought I would have anything to do with someone like Shi Yan.

